@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Obtener todos los grupos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/school-groups

###

### Obtener grupo por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/school-groups/1

###

### Crear grupo
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/school-groups
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Grupo F",
  "grade": "5°",
  "period": "2025",
  "status": "active"
}

###

### Actualizar grupo
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/school-groups/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Grupo F Actualizado",
  "status": "active"
}

###

### Eliminar grupo fisicamente
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/school-groups/1

###

### Eliminar grupo logicamente
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/school-groups/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "inactive"
}
